### =========================================
### AUTH
### =========================================
POST http://localhost:8087/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "password": "Admin@123"
}

### Refresh token (uses cookie from login)
POST http://localhost:8087/api/v1/auth/refresh-token

### Profile
GET http://localhost:8087/api/v1/auth/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### =========================================
### USERS (ADMIN)
### =========================================
GET http://localhost:8087/api/v1/users?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

GET http://localhost:8087/api/v1/users/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

PATCH http://localhost:8087/api/v1/users/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "role": "USER",
  "isActive": true
}

